{"word":"Λακωνικός","slug":"Λακωνικός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>Λακωνικός</b></el> <p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>Laconian</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>as <a href='S:Substantive'>Subst.</a>, <p/></div><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><el>ἡ Λακωνική</el> (<a href='S:subaudi, subaudito'>sub.</a> <el>γῆ</el>), <i>Laconia</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><el>Λακωνικαί</el> (<a href='S:subaudi, subaudito'>sub.</a> <el>ἐμβάδες</el>), <el>αἱ</el>, <i>Laconian shoes</i>, used by men, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><el>τὸ Λακωνικόν</el> <i>the state of Lacedaemon</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}